## 🌍 Hetchfund.com – Crowdfunding for Start-Up Innovation & Youth Empowerment 
<img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Hetchfund Preview" width="600"/>
 
**Tech Stack:** Angular, Python (Flask/FastAPI), Yoco Payments, Heroku  
**Type:** Full-Stack Web Application  
**Status:** 🚀 Live / In Development *(adjust as needed)*

### 📌 Overview  
Hetchfund.com is a full-stack crowdfunding platform built to support **innovative start-up businesses** while addressing the challenge of **rising youth unemployment**. The platform is designed to promote economic empowerment and entrepreneurial growth through seamless digital experiences.

### ✨ Key Features  
- 💻 Developed using **Angular** for a modern, responsive frontend.  
- 🐍 **Python backend** (Flask or FastAPI) powering core business logic and APIs.  
- 💳 **Integrated Yoco Payments**, allowing secure contributions from backers.  
- 👥 Enables **entrepreneurs to create campaigns**, raise capital, and showcase their ideas.  
- ⚙️ **Admin dashboard** for managing projects, users, and financials.  
- 🧭 **Streamlined user experience** with a clean, modern UI tailored to early-stage entrepreneurs and backers.  
- 🌍 Designed with a focus on **social impact**, especially targeting underserved youth and communities.

### 🛠️ What I Did  
- Led the **end-to-end development** of the platform architecture and UI.  
- Integrated third-party services like **Yoco** for payments and configured secure API endpoints.  
- Focused on building a platform that is **scalable, intuitive, and impact-driven**.  
- Managed deployment using **Heroku**, including environment setup and version control.
